        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>15 frontier AI models with disclosed training compute (FLOP) by publication date. Each dot represents one model release. Three clusters where multiple models share identical date and FLOP coordinates are annotated. Models without Epoch AI verified compute disclosures are not shown.</run>
